{"tid":873363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【港珠澳揭幕】呢張相爆亮點 網民驚：驟眼睇以為係神主牌！","createTime":"2018-10-23T11:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T18:20:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":179,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab6e25722b4f658e68f68509f770325bad0d7a7","tid":873363,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181023/large/1540287998_8047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181023%2Flarge%2F1540287998_8047.jpg&h=34b314cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋今日揭幕，揭幕典禮裝飾以一片紅色為主，椅子則佈上紅布，再貼上一張粉紅色紙張，上面以黑色毛筆字書體，寫上獲安排座位人士的姓名。不過，這個設計看上去有點詭異，有fb專頁開Po揶揄「儀式出現『神主牌MODE』？」<br />\nFb專頁「公關災難」帖文寫道，「【港珠澳大橋儀式出現「神主牌MODE」？ 】【咁都得系列】」，帖文貼上一張港珠澳大橋揭幕儀式，台下的座位安排照片，「唔只PIGLET同維尼，港珠澳大橋通車仲有呢一幕，男公關驟眼睇以為係神主牌又或者山墳，大吉利是咩....搵唔到林鄭月娥同梁振英個牌既（嘅）？#網絡欺凌」。<br />\n帖文出了短短半小時，就狼近百人讚好，「係咪大橋嘅死傷工友？」、「路過，幫林鄭念轉經」、「林奠同CY坐白色凳的」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181023/58827003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181023%2F58827003&d=YHjfK%2BayDGKMcIDSFjaTjxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=999dff99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181023%2F58827003&h=9522535f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181023/58827003</a>"},{"pid":"ebd1a02162713fdecf9da68c147e2b1069089626","tid":873363,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hk